  "title": "Most Holy Place",
  "comment": "The inner sanctuary of the tabernacle set up at Sinai and of Solomon's temple, where the ark of the covenant was kept. It is a symbol of the unapproachable presence of God.",
  "refgroup": null,
  "children": [],
